snippet.title: Glory of the Pandaria Raider - I Heard you Like Amber... [FROST MAGE SOLO] 8.0.1
snippet.description:
After watching some vids on how to solo it I decided to try out doing this with frost spec and water elemental. I had it tank the boss until she ran out of energy, and called the ads.
Burned the small ones down and then the big ones slowly, together (10sec).
Then she came back and I tried to burned her down before I got the 5 stacks but she got me and my water elemental finished the job :]

Special thanks to Trophy Gamer, for showing me how to get this achievement as a hunter.
Link to his video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2PehUBcjRlE

Like and subscribe if you liked this video!
